title: Voting for a new parliament begins in Egypt
text: Shows on WXOW Voting for a new parliament begins in Egypt (AP Photo/Nariman El-Mofty). An Egyptian traffic policeman looks at a woman standing outside the entrance of a polling center, before polls open at the first round of the parliamentary election in Cairo, Egypt, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. Arabic on the bann... (AP Photo/Hassan Ammar). Security forces stand guard in front a polling center during the Egyptian parliamentary election in Alexandria, Egypt, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (AP Photo/Hassan Ammar). Security forces pose for a picture as they stand guard in front of a polling station during the Egyptian parliamentary election in Alexandria, Egypt, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (AP Photo/Hassan Ammar). An Egyptian voter passes security forces to cast ballot at a polling station during the Egyptian parliamentary election in Alexandria, Egypt, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015. (AP Photo/Hassan Ammar). An Egyptian woman enters a polling center as an army soldier stands guard during the Egyptian parliamentary election in Alexandria, Egypt, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015.
